column33: [Conversational - A post/tweet that directly addresses another user(s) by asking/answering a question involving them. (@NameofFriend what can you say about this picture?)]
column34: [Promotional - A post/tweet on marketing or promoting an event, activity, contest, page/site, sale, and etc that urges the user to partake in an action. (Permission to post: for sale pre-loved items)]
column35: [Informational - A post/tweet that presents a topic or an update or live discussion of an event, reports news, or provides information. (Best travel spots in the Philippines #ILovePhil)]
column36: [Status - Answers the Twitter question "What's happening?' or the Facebook question "What's on your mind?" post. (NameofUser - feeling happy and blessed 'coz it's my birthday.)]
column37: [Phatic - Any post/tweet containing statements of greetings to the broader community in the social sites, undirected statement of opinion, or establishing sociability rather than communicating information or ideas. (Wishing everyone a Merry Christmas and a Happy New Year!)]
column38: [Unclassified - Posts/tweets that do not belong in any of the categories above.  (“~~~~OPA!~~~~~” Oh yeah! #RedHorseBeer)]
